        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 22 at 8:21PM CDT by NWS Midland/Odessa TX</headline>
        <description>At 821 PM CDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Lamesa, moving north at 10 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph and penny size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
Lamesa, Lamesa Municipal Airport, Los Ybanez, Tenmile, Arvana, Key,
and Sparenberg.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
